messageBody:
Oops... I've already spotted a problem in my QsConverter program
(placed in the files section earlier this week)... it isn't handling
hyphenated words properly. I'll try to find some time this coming
weekend to correct it and I'll upload the revision. If anyone else
finds any other bugs, please let me know.
Thanks,
Jeff
